<!--
=========================================================================
HolographicGlyphs.xaml - EVE Holographic Glyph Icon System
=========================================================================
Comprehensive minimalist glyph icon system for the Westworld-EVE fusion
interface. Features glowing vector icons optimized for holographic
display with scalable geometry and animated effects.

Features:
- EVE ship module and station iconography
- Minimalist glyph design language
- Scalable vector geometry
- Holographic glow effects
- Interactive animation states
- Performance-optimized rendering
- Consistent visual hierarchy

Author: Gideon Development Team
Created: June 21, 2025
=========================================================================
-->

